description:
Nikki D is having some self confidence issues. Seems as if she's feeling a bit inadequate about some of her lady parts. She thinks her lips, her breasts, her ass- all of it could be a little more full. So she seeks an opinion from her surgeon, Dr. Samuel O'Toole. After a preliminary examination, his findings prove inconclusive pending further investigation. Seems Samuel, ever the perfectionist, would like to do some internal exploration before coming up with his findings.

Enjoy!
title: The Doctor Is In
